amy Athletic Center]]\n|[[Toronto]], Ontario, Canada\n|[[reDRagon]] ([[Bobby Fish]] and Kyle O'Reilly) (c) vs. [[The Young Bucks]] (Matt Jackson and Nick Jackson) in a 2 out of 3 falls match for the ROH World Tag Team Championship\n|-\n|{{sort|40|40}}\n|December 7\n|[[Final Battle 2014]]\n|[[Terminal 5 (venue)|Terminal 5]] \n|[[New York City]], [[New York (state)|New York]] \n|Jay Briscoe (c) vs. Adam Cole in a [[Fight Without Honor]] for the ROH World Championship \n|-\n|}\n\n===2015===\n{| class=\"sortable wikitable succession-box\" style=\"font-size:85%;\"\n\n! width=4%| #\n! width=7%| Date\n! width=13%| Event\n! width=13%| Venue\n! width=13%| Location\n! width=50%| Main event\n|-\n\n|{{sort|41|41}}\n|March 1\n|[[ROH 13th Anniversary Show]]\n|[[Orleans Hotel & Casino]]\n|[[Las Vegas Valley|Las Vegas, Nevada]]\n|Jay Briscoe (c) vs. [[Tommaso Ciampa]] vs. Michael Elgin vs. [[Hanson (wrestler)|Hanson]] in a [[Professional wrestling match types|Four corner survival match]] for the ROH World Championship\n|-\n|{{sort|42|42}}\n|May 15\n|[[Global Wars '15]]\n|[[Ted Reeve Arena]]\n|[[Toronto|Toronto, Ontario]], Canada\n|ROH All Stars (Hanson, [[Raymond Rowe]], Jay Briscoe, Mark Briscoe and Roderick Strong) vs. [[Bullet Club]] (A.J. Styles, [[Luke Gallows|Doc Gallows]], [[Karl Anderson]], Matt Jackson and Nick Jackson) in a [[Professional wrestling tag team match types|Ten-man tag team match]]\n|-\n|{{sort|43|43}}\n|June 19\n|[[Best in the World 2015]]\n|[[Terminal 5 (venue)|Terminal 5]]\n|[[New York City|New York City, New York]]\n|ROH World Champion Jay Briscoe vs. ROH World Television Champion Jay Lethal in a [[Professional wrestling match types#Winner Takes All match|Winner Take All match]] for the ROH World Championship and the [[ROH World Television Championship]]\n|-\n|{{sort|44|44}}\n|July 24\n|[[Death Before Dishonor XIII]]\n|[[William J Meyers Pavilion]]\n|[[Baltimore|Baltimore, Maryland]]\n|Jay Lethal (c) vs. Roderick Strong for the ROH World Championship\n|-\n