lex Shelley]] and [[Chris Sabin]]) vs. The Young Bucks (Matt Jackson and Nick Jackson) in [[Ladder match|Ladder War VI]] for the ROH World Tag Team Championship\n|-\n|{{sort|52|52}}\n|December 2 \n|[[Final Battle (2016)|Final Battle]]\n|[[Hammerstein Ballroom]]\n|New York, New York\n|Adam Cole (c) vs. Kyle O'Reilly for the ROH World Championship\n|-\n|}\n\n===2017===\n{| class=\"sortable wikitable succession-box\" style=\"font-size:85%;\"\n\n! width=4%| #\n! width=7%| Date\n! width=13%| Event\n! width=13%| Venue\n! width=13%| Location\n! width=50%| Main event\n|-\n\n|{{sort|53|53}}\n|March 10\n|[[ROH 15th Anniversary Show]]\n|[[Sam's Town Hotel and Gambling Hall, Las Vegas|Sam's Town Hotel & Gambling Hall]]\n|[[Las Vegas Valley|Las Vegas, Nevada]]\n|Adam Cole (c) vs. Christopher Daniels for the ROH World Championship\n|-\n|{{sort|54|54}}\n|April 1\n|[[Supercard of Honor XI]]\n|[[Lakeland Center]]\n|[[Lakeland, Florida]]\n|[[The Hardy Boyz|The Hardys]] ([[Jeff Hardy|Jeff]] and [[Matt Hardy]]) (c) vs. The Young Bucks (Matt and Nick Jackson) in a [[ladder match]] for the ROH World Tag Team Championship\n|-\n|{{sort|55|55}}\n|May 12\n|[[ROH/NJPW War of the Worlds (2017)|War of the Worlds]]\n|[[Hammerstein Ballroom]]\n|[[New York City, New York]]\n|Christopher Daniels (c) vs. [[Cody Rhodes|Cody]] vs. Jay Lethal for the ROH World Championship\n|-\n|{{sort|56|56}}\n|June 23\n|[[Best in the World (2017)|Best in the World]]\n|[[Lowell Memorial Auditorium]]\n|[[Lowell, Massachusetts]]\n|Christopher Daniels (c) vs. Cody for the ROH World Championship\n|-\n|{{sort|57|57}}\n|August 19\n|[[War of the Worlds UK: Liverpool]]\n|[[Liverpool Olympia]]\n|[[Liverpool]], England\n|Cody (c) vs. [[Seiya Sanada|Sanada]] for the ROH World Championship\n|-\n|{{sort|58|58}}\n|September 22\n|[[Death Before Dishonor XV]]\n|[[Sam's Town Hotel and Gambling Hall, Las Vegas|Sam's Town Hotel & Gambling Hall]]\n|[[Las Vegas Valley|Las Vegas, Nevada]]\n|Cody (c) vs. [[Minoru Suzuki]] for the ROH World 